\pard\fi-360\li1440\tx1440\f2 o\tab\f0 DeploymentPlan Interpreter: The implementation detail of a component instance is now determined by the component instance\rquote s type, and not its name. Selecting the implementation detail based on the component instance\rquote s name was a problem when a subtype of a component, or any component instance, was given the incorrect name. \par
\pard\fi-360\li1440\f2 o\tab\f0 DeploymentPlan Interpreter: The type information for monolithic components of component assembly instances that were contained in another component assemblies was not handled correctly.\par
